Paul,

Don't know about the UK, but the Oz delivery busses from '74, at least, had the 
hatch in the rear deck above the engine bay, for access to the carbs.

The picture in the link below SORT of shows the hatch.

http://www.geocities.com/MotorCity/Garage/1811/pictures/engine.jpg

